      • resize

        void resize(int num,
          ExpandDirection dir)
        Resizes the gate's portal volume by the specified number of blocks in the specified direction.

        The number of blocks can be negative.

        Parameters:
        num - the number of blocks to add
        dir - the direction to add blocks
